<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cheap-adv">cheap <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tʃiːp/    美 /tʃiːp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>便宜地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Look in the paper to see if there are any computers <strong>going cheap</strong>.
看看宣传单上是否有电脑在降价出售。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Violins like this <strong>don’t come cheap</strong>.
像这样的小提琴不会便宜。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>cheaply /'tʃiːpli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Bread is c<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ in this shop; it costs twice as much across the street.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. cheap / cheaper  </p></div>